Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Permission denied for system commands

Solution: Some commands may require sudo. Update scripts to handle this or run specific commands manually
Issue: Missing Python modules

Solution: Ensure virtual environment is activated: source ~/compliance-lab/venv/bin/activate
Issue: Empty evidence collection

Solution: Run generate_sample_data.sh first to create test data
Issue: JSON parsing errors

Solution: Validate JSON syntax using jq before processing
